<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Scodeno Indonesia — Industrial Networking Solutions</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Scodeno Indonesia — Exclusive distributor of Scodeno industrial switches. Managed, unmanaged, PoE, and data center networking solutions for Indonesian industry.">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      /* Brand */
      --blue:        #0068B4;
      --blue-light:  #0095E0;
      --blue-dark:   #004A82;
      --blue-glow:   rgba(0, 104, 180, 0.20);

      /* Surfaces */
      --black:       #0A0E14;
      --near-black:  #141A22;
      --dark-card:   #1A202A;
      --white:       #FFFFFF;
      --off-white:   #F5F7FA;
      --gray-100:    #E8ECF0;
      --gray-200:    #C8CDD4;
      --gray-300:    #9BA2AB;
      --gray-400:    #6B7280;
      --gray-500:    #4B5563;

      /* Semantic */
      --text-dark:   #1A1A1A;
      --text-light:  #E2E8F0;
      --text-muted:  #9BA2AB;

      /* Spacing */
      --space-xs: 4px;
      --space-sm: 8px;
      --space-md: 16px;
      --space-lg: 24px;
      --space-xl: 32px;
      --space-2xl: 48px;
      --space-3xl: 64px;
      --space-4xl: 96px;

      /* Radius */
      --radius-sm: 2px;
      --radius-md: 4px;
      --radius-lg: 8px;

      /* Max width */
      --content-max: 1200px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      background: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* ── Typography ── */
    h1, h2, h3, h4 { font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; }
    h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem); letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.25rem); letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; }
    p  { color: var(--gray-500); }

    /* ── Navigation ── */
    .nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(10, 14, 20, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: var(--content-max); margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg); height: 64px;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    }
    .nav-logo-text { color: var(--white); }
    .nav-logo-indonesia { color: var(--blue-light); margin-left: 4px; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: var(--space-xl); list-style: none; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--gray-200); text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }

    /* Dropdown */
    .nav-dropdown { position: relative; }
    .nav-dropdown > a { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
    .nav-dropdown > a::after { content: '▾'; font-size: 0.625rem; margin-left: 2px; }
    .nav-dropdown-menu {
      position: absolute; top: 100%; left: 0; min-width: 200px;
      background: var(--dark-card); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 6px; padding: 6px 0; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden;
      transform: translateY(4px); transition: all 0.18s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    }
    .nav-dropdown:hover .nav-dropdown-menu { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; transform: translateY(0); }
    .nav-dropdown-menu a {
      display: block; padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 0.8125rem;
      color: var(--gray-300); border-radius: 0;
    }
    .nav-dropdown-menu a:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); color: var(--white); }

    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--blue); color: var(--white);
      padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8125rem; text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--blue-light); }

    /* ── Sections ── */
    .section { padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-lg); }
    .section-dark { background: var(--black); color: var(--text-light); }
    .section-dark p { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .section-light { background: var(--white); }
    .section-offset { background: var(--off-white); }
    .container { max-width: var(--content-max); margin: 0 auto; }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      background: var(--black);
      color: var(--white);
      min-height: 90vh;
      display: flex; align-items: center;
      padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-lg);
      padding-top: calc(64px + var(--space-3xl));
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: -40%; right: -20%;
      width: 700px; height: 700px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--blue-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      display: inline-block; color: var(--blue-light);
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8125rem; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }
    .hero h1 { margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    }
    .hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-sm);
      padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9375rem; text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.15s; cursor: pointer; border: none;
    }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--blue); color: var(--white); }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--blue-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent; color: var(--white);
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--white); }

    /* ── Section Headers ── */
    .section-label {
      display: inline-block; color: var(--blue-light);
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.8125rem; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }
    .section-header {
      text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    }
    .section-header h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
    .section-header p {
      max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.0625rem;
    }

    /* ── Product Grid ── */
    .product-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }
    .product-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: var(--space-xl);
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .product-card::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
      background: var(--blue);
    }
    .product-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .product-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px; background: rgba(0,104,180,0.08);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: var(--blue); font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
    .product-card h3 { margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
    .product-card p { font-size: 0.9375rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
    .product-link {
      color: var(--blue); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.875rem;
      text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
    }
    .product-link:hover { color: var(--blue-light); }

    /* ── Stats Row ── */
    .stats-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-xl); text-align: center;
    }
    .stat-value {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--white); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    }
    .stat-value .accent { color: var(--blue-light); }
    .stat-label { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9375rem; }

    /* ── Article Grid ── */
    .article-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }
    .article-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md); overflow: hidden;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .article-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .article-body { padding: var(--space-lg); }
    .article-tag {
      display: inline-block; background: rgba(0,104,180,0.08);
      color: var(--blue); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600;
      padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 2px; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .article-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .article-card p {
      font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }
    .article-meta {
      font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--gray-400);
      display: flex; gap: var(--space-md);
    }

    /* ── CTA Section ── */
    .cta-section {
      background: var(--black);
      color: var(--white);
      text-align: center;
      padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-lg);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-section::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -40%; left: -20%;
      width: 600px; height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--blue-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cta-section .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .cta-section h2 { margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
    .cta-section p {
      color: var(--text-muted); max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl); font-size: 1.0625rem;
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .footer {
      background: var(--near-black);
      color: var(--text-muted);
      padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-lg) var(--space-xl);
    }
    .footer-grid {
      max-width: var(--content-max); margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .footer-brand h3 { color: var(--white); font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
    .footer-brand p { font-size: 0.875rem; }
    .footer-col h4 {
      color: var(--white); font-size: 0.8125rem; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }
    .footer-col a {
      display: block; color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.875rem; padding: 4px 0; transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--white); }
    .footer-bottom {
      max-width: var(--content-max); margin: 0 auto;
      padding-top: var(--space-lg);
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      font-size: 0.8125rem;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .hero-buttons { flex-direction: column; }
      .btn { justify-content: center; }
      .section { padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-md); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-md); text-align: center; }
    }

    /* ── About Section ── */
    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-3xl);
      align-items: center;
    }
    .about-grid h3 { margin-bottom: var(--space-md); color: var(--white); }
    .about-grid p { margin-bottom: var(--space-md); font-size: 1.0625rem; }
    .about-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
      margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    }
    .about-stat {
      background: var(--dark-card);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--space-lg);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .about-stat-value {
      font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--white); line-height: 1;
    }
    .about-stat-value .blue { color: var(--blue-light); }
    .about-stat-label { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-xs); }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .about-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    /* ── Utils ── */
    .text-accent { color: var(--blue-light); }
    .sr-only { position: absolute; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; clip: rect(0,0,0,0); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
        <img src="logo.png" alt="Scodeno" class="nav-logo-img" style="height:36px; width:auto;">
        <span class="nav-logo-text">Scodeno<span class="nav-logo-indonesia">Indonesia</span></span>
      </a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li class="nav-dropdown">
          <a href="#products">Products</a>
          <div class="nav-dropdown-menu">
            <a href="#products">Unmanaged Switches</a>
            <a href="#products">Managed Switches</a>
            <a href="#products">PoE Switches</a>
            <a href="#products">Data Center</a>
            <a href="#products">xPON / Fiber</a>
            <a href="#products">Smart Box &amp; IoT</a>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-dropdown">
          <a href="#articles">Articles</a>
          <div class="nav-dropdown-menu">
            <a href="#articles-fundamental">Fundamental</a>
            <a href="#articles-selection-guide">Selection Guide</a>
            <a href="#articles-technology">Technology</a>
            <a href="#articles-deployment">Deployment</a>
            <a href="#articles-network-design">Network Design</a>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Request Quote</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero" id="home">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Exclusive Distributor for Indonesia</span>
      <h1>Industrial Networking<br>Built for Demanding<br>Environments</h1>
      <p>
        From factory floors to power utilities — Scodeno delivers rugged, reliable industrial switches engineered for 24/7 operation in the toughest conditions.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#products" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Products</a>
        <a href="#articles" class="btn btn-outline">Read Technical Articles</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Products -->
  <section class="section section-light" id="products">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Product Categories</span>
        <h2>Industrial Switch Portfolio</h2>
        <p>From plug-and-play unmanaged switches to advanced Layer 3 managed solutions — built for industrial environments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="product-grid">

        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M8 8h8M8 12h8M8 16h5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Unmanaged Industrial Switches</h3>
          <p>Plug-and-play DIN-rail switches. Wide temperature -40°C to 75°C, IP40 rated. Available in 4, 5, 8, and 16 ports.</p>
          <a href="#products" class="product-link">View Series &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><circle cx="7" cy="8" r="1.5"/><circle cx="7" cy="12" r="1.5"/><path d="M11 8h7M11 12h7M11 16h4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Managed Industrial Switches</h3>
          <p>Layer 2/3 managed switches with VLAN, QoS, SNMP, and ERPS ring redundancy. Full network control for critical infrastructure.</p>
          <a href="#products" class="product-link">View Series &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M7 8l5 4-5 4"/><path d="M14 16h3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>PoE Industrial Switches</h3>
          <p>Power over Ethernet up to 90W per port (PoE++). Ideal for IP cameras, wireless APs, and IoT devices in remote locations.</p>
          <a href="#products" class="product-link">View Series &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="1" y="3" width="22" height="18" rx="2"/><rect x="5" y="7" width="14" height="10" rx="1"/><line x1="12" y1="7" x2="12" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Data Center Switches</h3>
          <p>High-density 10G/25G/100G switches. Marvell, Broadcom, and Centec platforms. Redundant power, smart cooling.</p>
          <a href="#products" class="product-link">View Series &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 014 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4 10"/><path d="M2 12h20"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>xPON / Fiber Solutions</h3>
          <p>OLT, ONU, and PON modules. Full fiber network solutions for campus and metro deployments.</p>
          <a href="#products" class="product-link">View Series &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="6" width="18" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M7 10h4M7 14h2M14 10h3M14 14h3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Smart Box & IoT</h3>
          <p>Solar-powered IoT smart boxes with integrated remote communication. All-in-one power and connectivity for field deployments.</p>
          <a href="#products" class="product-link">View Series &rarr;</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Articles -->
  <section class="section section-offset" id="articles">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">Knowledge Hub</span>
        <h2>Artikel Teknis Industrial Networking</h2>
        <p>Panduan praktis dan analisis mendalam tentang infrastruktur jaringan industri — ditulis oleh engineer, untuk engineer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="article-grid">

        <article class="article-card">
          <a href="articles/Week_01_kenapa-industrial-switch-menggunakan-desain-fanless.html" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="article-body">
            <span class="article-tag">Fundamental</span>
            <h3>Kenapa Industrial Switch Menggunakan Desain Fanless</h3>
            <p>Mengapa desain tanpa kipas menjadi standar emas dalam rugged switch design untuk keandalan jangka panjang.</p>
            <div class="article-meta"><span>10 min read</span><span>Design</span></div>
          </div>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="article-card">
          <a href="articles/Week_02_apa-itu-din-rail-industrial-switch-dan-mengapa-banyak-dipakai-di-pabrik.html" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="article-body">
            <span class="article-tag">Fundamental</span>
            <h3>Apa Itu DIN-Rail Industrial Switch dan Mengapa Banyak Dipakai di Pabrik</h3>
            <p>Format perangkat yang mendominasi panel kontrol di seluruh dunia — ringkas, tangguh, dan efisien.</p>
            <div class="article-meta"><span>12 min read</span><span>Hardware</span></div>
          </div>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="article-card">
          <a href="articles/Week_03_ip-rating-pada-industrial-ethernet-switch-apa-artinya.html" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="article-body">
            <span class="article-tag">Fundamental</span>
            <h3>IP Rating pada Industrial Ethernet Switch: Apa Artinya?</h3>
            <p>Memahami kode IP dari IP30 hingga IP67 — standar internasional yang menjamin ketahanan enclosure.</p>
            <div class="article-meta"><span>8 min read</span><span>Standards</span></div>
          </div>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="article-card">
          <a href="articles/Week_04_industrial-gigabit-switch-vs-fast-ethernet-switch.html" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="article-body">
            <span class="article-tag">Selection Guide</span>
            <h3>Industrial Gigabit Switch vs Fast Ethernet Switch</h3>
            <p>Memilih antara kecepatan, determinisme jaringan, dan biaya total sepanjang usia pabrik.</p>
            <div class="article-meta"><span>7 min read</span><span>Performance</span></div>
          </div>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="article-card">
